long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Aggregates video watch speed statistics and automatically sets your watch speed.

Takes into account the speed at which other users watch videos - be more productive by speeding through slower videos! 

To use (Supports YouTube only right now):

Speeds are set automatically. Since the YT video player has an issue with setting playback speeds ( https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/130638003 ), changes will not reflect in the YouTube player but the speed IS set.

Note: Report any errors in the console.
